Package ui

Class Summary
AgentInfoPanel A panel that displays the Entity and Agent specific data about a give agent.
AgentPanel The main Agent GUI widget, created and maintained by the respective agent.
GADialog The GA editor wizard dialog.
GenePanel A GUI widget created and maintained by its respective Gene.
ImagePanel JPanel with a background image.
MainWindow The main GUI container and entry point of execution in Symbibots.
SidePanel Main tabbed container for holding user panels.
